\pard\sa300\f0\fs44\b\cf1 Manual: Ayo -- Evaluation and Writeup\b0\cf0\par
\pard\sa160\f0\fs22 Covers Tasks 8-11 of spec/00-project-roadmap.md. Depends on Paul's trained model(s) and test-set predictions. This is the last stage -- you close out the project.\par
\pard\sa160\f0\fs22 Relevant skills: test (evaluation), data (interpretation), review (final pass), reflection (closing journal entry).\par
\pard\sa160\f0\fs22 You can start early: write the evaluation script against placeholder predictions so you're not idle waiting on Paul, then swap in his real model/test_predictions.csv when ready.\par
\pard\sb320\sa200\f0\fs32\b\cf1 Suggested branches\b0\cf0\par
\pard\sa160\f0\fs22 One branch per task, following the repo's existing feat--<name> convention.\par
\pard\li480\fi-240\f0\fs22\bullet\tab Task 8 (Evaluation): feat--model-evaluation\par
\pard\li480\fi-240\f0\fs22\bullet\tab Task 9 (Interpretation): feat--model-interpretation\par
